The TempFix External Fixation System by DePuy Trauma & Extremities is a line of staged
protocol solutions for initial treatment of complex fractures of the distal femur, proximal tibia
and distal tibia.
The TempFix External Fixation System is a cost-effective option for early treatment of peri-
articular fractures of the knee and ankle. Hospital costs are minimized as the need for
ransfixing Pin
sterilization and frame assembly is eliminated. This reduces time spent by OR personnel
